LLVM SDK @LLVM_VERSION@

Target triple: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@
Bootstrap LLVM version: @BOOTSTRAP_LLVM_VERSION@

This SDK intentionally builds LLVM without clang, lld, or clang-tools-extra.
It includes LLVM headers, LLVM tools, libLLVM, libLTO, and the external
dependency headers, libraries, and shared data used to build them.
Dependency package executables are intentionally not shipped in this SDK.

LLVM target backends:
  @LLVM_TARGETS@

LLVM experimental target backends:
  @LLVM_EXPERIMENTAL_TARGETS@
